summary: This mod is very simple and easy to use. It is used to replace the Default level up sound in Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Hello there again Nexus

Includes: Final Fantasy and Legend of Zelda sounds.

This mod is very simple and easy to use. It is used to replace the Default level up sound in Skyrim.

Im currently experimenting with sounds for a previous mod I have made and this opportunity came about.

All you have to do is choose the type of sound you want then copy the \"Sound\" folder from that folder
 
you choose to your Data folder and your done.

Credit for these sounds goes to: 

------------------
Square Enix
------------------
Nintendo
------------------

I did not Create them I only Packaged them for you to use in your Skyrim

This is only the 1.0 Version there will be more additions later on.

All I ask is for anyone who has an idea for a good addition to post it :)

Have fun guys <3
author: MissAshlay
